content:
Your company's loyalty program can now partner with up to 50,000 brands. With more partners onboarded, the loyalty program can offer members rewards for a more diverse range of products and run varied joint promotions. Earlier, a loyalty program could onboard only 10,000 partners.

This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer editions where Loyalty Management - Growth or Loyalty Management - Advanced is enabled.

Manage Loyalty Program Partners (can be outdated or unavailable during release preview)
title: Increase Loyalty Program's Appeal with More Brands
